data.description: Welcome to your new home in Providence Crossing. Fall in love from the time you pull up to 375 Delaware River Dr! Enter into your formal living room with luxary vinyl plank flooring. As you continue through the home you'll enter the large open family room  with a gas fireplace to cozy up to. You'll also enjoy the shiplap detail, wood mantle, and beautiful built-in shelving. This space is easy for entertaining with a dry bar and wine fridge.  The spacious family room flows right into the large kitchen. You'll love the the beautiful backsplash, granite countertops, and abundant counterspace with the large island! The kitchen over looks the breakfast nook that includes high bar seating. Off off the kitchen you'll conveniently find the mud room with built in cubbies leading to the garage. Off of the breakfast nook you'll enjoy the screened in porch with a built-in bar that leads to a paver patio and fenced in back yard. How convenient that your new home backs to open space and the park! Head upstairs to find the gracious sized bedrooms and the laundry room! The master bedroom has a board and batten accent wall, en suite with a jetted tub to relax in, double sink, stand-up shower, and a huge walk-in closet! There are three more great sized bedrooms with a shared hall bathroom. The basement has been partially finished with two separate living spaces and an unfinished area for storage or your home gym! Make sure you come by to experience this beauty for yourself!
